INSERT INTO message (id, channelId, userId, message, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES ('1224804858331398235', '1178822630225227818', '139462049976549377', '# Cold Email #1\n\n## Title: ‚ÄúSolving Communication + AI‚Äù\n\nHello I am Ben, CEO of https://www.croak.ai we are building a new communication app, similiar to Microsoft Teams, but are using AI to 10x producivity. Between all the redudant meetings, bloated games-of-telephone between teams, and lost information buried in channels, AI is a perfect way to fix these problems.\n\nYou‚Äôre probably thinking Slack and Teams already have the data, why the hell would we try to compete? Well me and my cofounder discovered that because of the data-storage decisions those companies made 10 years ago and the unstructured nature of communication, it will be a massive engineering undertaking, and an even bigger security risk, to properly serve AI communication data. This is why Slack‚Äôs AI features they launched are very limited.\n\nThat‚Äôs why we are building croak from the ground up to securely serve AI communication data, and in only 2 months of development we have proved our theories on what it takes to give AI communication data. \n\nWould you like to schedule a meeting and learn more about Croak? We are currently raising our pre-seed round thanks!\n\n# Cold Email #2 - shorter\n\n## Title: ‚ÄúSolving Communication + AI‚Äù\n\nHello I am Ben, CEO of https://www.croak.ai we are building a new communication app, similiar to Microsoft Teams or Slack, but are using AI to 10x productivity. We are approaching our communication data  differently than Slack or Teams, which allow us to answer questions like ‚ÄúWhat was Nick doing last week‚Äù.\n\nI think you‚Äôd be a great investor because {BLAH BLAH BLAH}. We have been building the product since January and we are at the point where we‚Äôve proven our data-storage + AI conjecture. Can we meet and discuss this? Thanks!', 1712086634000, 1712086634000);
